<!--
Fullscreen interactive birthday site for Chelsea (single-file)
Save as `index.html`. Open on phone for best experience.
Replace placeholder images in `images/` and replace `music/most-beautiful-thing.mp3` with your own file (you must supply the song file yourself).

Features:
- Fullscreen staged slides (Welcome → Menu → Memories (5 slides) → Letter)
- Two big icons (Memories, Letter)
- Scroll/swipe or tap 'Next' to transition slides (page doesn't scroll normally)
- Soft paper texture, floating hearts, small heart transitions between memories
- Mobile-first, optimized for touch
- Minimal confetti (only small hearts)

Note about music: browsers often block autoplay. The music will start after the first user gesture (pressing "Yes please"), and there is a mute/play toggle in the bottom-right.
-->

