              <p>Happy Birthday, Chelsea. 🥰 I hope today fills you with laughter, little surprises, and the kind of joy you give to everyone around you. I don’t want to rush anything, but I do want you to know how much I cherish you and how excited I am for all the small moments we haven’t had yet.</p>
